				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Bard, monk, cleric trio<a name="43335"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jun 1 04 5:29 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I've been running LDoN's for quite a while now with 2 friends. We're all around the same lvl (45), and have gotten to know each others playing styles well.
<br />
My question is, would it be possible to complete a high risk adventure with this trio at our level?
<br />
We've not tried it yet but plan to tonight, and would like some hypothetical input from you good people as to how long we'd last<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" />
<br />
Before i forget we're all slightly twinked in bazaar gear, but nothing too excessive. 
<br />
Thanks in advance.<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" /></span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="SmallText"><hr size="1" align="left" width="15%"><i>~But then there's a moment like tonight, a profound and transcendent experience, the feeling as if a door has opened, and it's all because of those instruments, those incredible, magical instruments.~ </i>
</span></td>
